org.sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT users.id) FROM users INNER JOIN members ON members.user_id = users.id WHERE users.type IN ('User', 'AnonymousUser') AND users.status = "$1" AND members.project_id = 1

rewrites.sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT users.id) FROM users INNER JOIN members ON members.user_id = users.id WHERE users.type IN ('User', 'AnonymousUser') AND users.status = "$1" AND members.project_id = 1 LIMIT 1
